Everyday Health Inc., formerly Waterfront Media, operates more than 25 websites that provide health tips and solutions, including pregnancy and diet advice to medical condition management information. These sites include www.everydayhealth.com, www.whattoexpect.com, www.southbeachdiet.com and www.jillianmichaels.com.
The information technology department at Everyday Health Inc. provides day-to-day technical support for all employees.

The IT department is classified by several smaller areas of specialty. Senior IT executives oversee software development and technology operations. Additional IT managers are responsible for the IT… MoreThe information technology department at Everyday Health Inc. provides day-to-day technical support for all employees.

The IT department is classified by several smaller areas of specialty. Senior IT executives oversee software development and technology operations. Additional IT managers are responsible for the IT help desk, desktop support, software development, and IT Project Management.

The company is constantly developing and maintaining its network of sites. In December 2010, Everyday Health also acquired MedPage Today, and its partner website KevinMD.com.





